Enhancement: `restic repair packs` can handle missing packfiles

In the past, deleted packfiles could not be repaired with the `restic check` and
`restic repair packs` command, since a missing packfile triggered an error exit
and not the repair procedure.

these commands now treat missing packfiles the same way as damaged packfiles are treated.
Missing packfiles can now "removed" correctly, by updating the master index.

